{"tid":1478123,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上熱門] 我地要學識從失敗中企返起身","createTime":"2019-08-16T11:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:51:02.000Z","uid":2634,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2270dd3515c5bf69c85b1d33fc5296e9d20202df","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:20:42.000Z","msg":"***重Post係政事台***<br />\n<br />\n2019.08.16 (五)<br />\n由6.9到今日，我地嘅士氣同支持度無可否認會差左同失去左小量中年和理非支持，加上今日喺街上見人道歉，希望大家可以聽我講幾句。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">「你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣」(蔡英文，2012)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1. 不要圍爐，要做高質人<br />\n以前我哋會笑啲藍絲冇腦，咩都唔FC好易俾人呃。經過8.13有好多中間派和理非同淺黃都會覺得民意有逆轉，而唔會再出聲住。我地要<strong>接受事實</strong>同改善，而唔係極端化，唔好令自己變成藍絲一樣咁低質。連登係一個好好嘅平台但同時我地都要去第二啲平台(甚至藍絲Page)睇下其他人諗咩。(--&gt;知己知彼加強文宣，<strong>暫緩</strong>不合作運動以減少我地俾位人入嘅機會，增加民意基礎，並非割席分化)<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/297/abd/297abd76f61044aabdb1da8fcca48720e72cca57_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F297%2Fabd%2F297abd76f61044aabdb1da8fcca48720e72cca57_n.jpg&h=f29fed38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 爭取更多中間和理非支持<br />\n我相信大家身邊有好多啱啱覺醒嘅親戚，佢地初次接觸政治好易轉軚。經過8.13之後佢地都唔敢再講佢地支持學生，我地唔可以失去左依班人，如果唔係就等於引火自焚。以今日嘅局面，我諗8.18遊行有50萬人我都偷笑。大家係咪想見到咁肉酸嘅局面？所以我地一定一定唔可以冇左佢地嘅支持！<br />\n<br />\n3.搞清楚所有概念<br />\n如果大家有讀過中學通識，搞唔清搞唔明重要概念就玩完啦。今場運動都係一樣，我認為「不分化不割席」唔係解咩都唔出聲，如果你係和理非，你可以同勇武不割席，大家有種暗中關係(你懂的)，但唔係唔聽對方俾你嘅意見，好似有人認為勇武應該暫時退場係分化割席，但係你理性d諗下，除左勇武派自己人，社會大眾嘅接受程度係點樣？你睇到依度可能覺得我係「鬼」，但我始終覺得一場運動係長時間捉對家錯處，而唔係自己不斷俾位人入。暫緩不合作運動同勇武暫時退場唔係代表我地嘅方向同行動錯，唔係永遠唔會再做，而係對家今日已經拆穿左我地嘅玩法，不斷用我地嘅行動去打擊我地嘅支持度同民意基礎(包括外國遊客)。請大家諗清楚！<br />\n<br />\n我只係一個廢青，不喜勿插，支持理討論！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0WQd7h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0WQd7h.gif&h=2f8b1f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f05ea1d97968243468937c4f767f6ba186510e8c","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>「你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣。你可以悲傷，但是不要放棄，因為明天起來，我們要像過去四年一樣的勇敢，心裏充滿着希望。因為，我們必須勇敢地扛起這個國家的責任，我們必須樂觀地，繼續為台灣這塊土地打拼。」<br />\n「有一天，我們會再回來，我們不會放棄。」<br />\n---2012年蔡英文敗選後發言---</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2e7d59524816a33cb1355b472bb02ea031079085","tid":1478123,"uid":18596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"同意！<br />\n各有各做時，發現問題，唔需要指責，只需要去改善。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808aedd163a0e2ddf0d529b14cc62d9659f0c317","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e7d59524816a33cb1355b472bb02ea031079085","tid":1478123,"uid":18596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"同意！<br />\n各有各做時，發現問題，唔需要指責，只需要去改善。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dfb9bb1b19581131695e22dd80016072ae9daa","tid":1478123,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f05ea1d97968243468937c4f767f6ba186510e8c","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>「你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣。你可以悲傷，但是不要放棄，因為明天起來，我們要像過去四年一樣的勇敢，心裏充滿着希望。因為，我們必須勇敢地扛起這個國家的責任，我們必須樂觀地，繼續為台灣這塊土地打拼。」<br />\n「有一天，我們會再回來，我們不會放棄。」<br />\n---2012年蔡英文敗選後發言---</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2872841b9b52d104dee9080c09b99ca31a36ba","tid":1478123,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:33:01.000Z","msg":"[假架d奶] 守護動物同民賤聯fd底<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cae44f5bf859df5554556bb2e32c4c3c2a75d47d","tid":1478123,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:38:18.000Z","msg":"今日同公司比較大年紀既同事傾過 點解最近會考慮少啲出黎遊行 其中一個考慮因素係太危險 <br />\n事實上 一個屋企有老有幼既人面對 警察無理既暴力 真係會退卻 無疑警犬既阻嚇普通市民出黎係好成功<br />\n若果 818人數係未如理想 我希望各位手足都唔好洩氣"},{"pid":"b151b32f2d42cccc11fec2cce7cccb42034dc44e","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58670f3e1bfa12f04fe413ef3819b5c33b85d264","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8.18 迫爆維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"85cf591a7b044b255599ede08988495a4b515184","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485b9c8baea3fd791d3332dca7079b828236cfa9","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5b5b7caab991504ac76a25a5157f16d7343a62","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:42:58.000Z","msg":"8.18<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1808e1277ca4ee42d0c8c5586ddc558f84bba05c","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8.18 迫爆維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"990c3b01473d31341198b24fce41c0de477e0778","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d679271f9ab5a5dad962cfe637a4d6cfb4b9525","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7f41cbfaf79d683caaead18c89122cde03e59f","tid":1478123,"uid":2634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}